headline: Leidos, global partners to boost NATO capabilities through cloud modernization
summary: A Leidos-led (NYSE: LDOS) modernization initiative, involving companies from France, Germany, Italy, and the U.K., aims to enhance NATO's IT infrastructure. The project is designed to improve resilience against cyber threats and increase efficiency and scalability, in support of NATO digital transformation.
